<div class="poster">
<h4>
<img src="Themes/celeste/images/useroff.gif" alt="离线"/>
<a href="?PHPSESSID=d02c2b8ebfdf44378e526f6c0f474323&amp;action=profile;u=6105" title="检视会员资料:  聪明伶俐琪露诺">聪明伶俐琪露诺</a>
